flowchart LR
    CFG[configs/]
    CLI[src/cli/]
    EXP[src/experiments/]

    DIN[data/raw + data/processed\nWEJSCIE]
    MOUT[models/\nWYJSCIE]
    ROUT[reports/\nWYJSCIE]
    TESTS[tests/]

    CFG --> CLI
    CLI --> EXP
    DIN --> EXP

    EXP --> FETCH[fetch]
    FETCH --> PRE[preprocess]
    PRE --> TRAIN[train]
    TRAIN --> EVAL[evaluate]
    EVAL --> VIZ[visualize]
    VIZ --> CMP[compare]

    PRE --> DIN
    TRAIN --> MOUT
    EVAL --> ROUT
    VIZ --> ROUT
    CMP --> ROUT

    TESTS -. weryfikuja .-> CLI
    TESTS -. weryfikuja .-> EXP
    TESTS -. weryfikuja .-> CFG
